.TH "pmcraid_copy_sglist" 9 "pmcraid_copy_sglist" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
pmcraid_copy_sglist \- Copy user buffer to kernel buffer's SG list
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" pmcraid_copy_sglist
.BI "(struct pmcraid_sglist *sglist "  ","
.BI "void __user *buffer "  ","
.BI "u32 len "  ","
.BI "int direction "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "sglist" 12
scatter/gather list pointer
.IP "buffer" 12
buffer pointer
.IP "len" 12
buffer length
.IP "direction" 12
data transfer direction
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Copy a user buffer into a buffer allocated by pmcraid_alloc_sglist

Return value:
0 on success / other on failure
